{"tid":1095820,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家身邊有無啲friend成日懶有幽默咁？","createTime":"2019-04-07T09:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T10:21:58.000Z","uid":175851,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"64113cc6566fb4604db45d38b3a0c08f05c5f39a","tid":1095820,"uid":175851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:54:58.000Z","msg":"之前一班人放飯嘅時候係度討論緊食咩<br />\n<br />\n有個<span style=\"color: red;\">friend</span>話不如陽錯<br />\n<br />\n我心惗：乜野陽錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其他人都唔知<span style=\"color: red;\">佢</span>講緊乜<br />\n<br />\n然後<span style=\"color: red;\">佢</span>話：飲茶啊，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飲茶陽錯！</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有次我地一大班人行緊嘅時候有另外一個friend被人踩到個鞋踭<br />\n<br />\n個friend向後望著其他人，其他人就話唔係佢地踩<br />\n<br />\n然後<span style=\"color: red;\">佢</span>走埋黎話：佢地真係無辜<br />\n<br />\n再補多句話個friend：你就有辜啦，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死有餘辜啊！</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然偶然惗番都覺得有啲幾搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9047eccbd141e3ea1f4a4e6b1f2ce3dc8a513519","tid":1095820,"uid":223778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:56:34.000Z","msg":"0"},{"pid":"4782bc739ebaa4d457c7a303ecfa79654f6a1c2d","tid":1095820,"uid":3852,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:57:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">你</span>做乜撚嘢"},{"pid":"ea14bb59db6570281b12bd79e01a23e1a75a661c","tid":1095820,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"幾時死"},{"pid":"7495a4ff9df51f3aaadc108900b68a32d69eba19","tid":1095820,"uid":175851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4782bc739ebaa4d457c7a303ecfa79654f6a1c2d","tid":1095820,"uid":3852,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:57:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">你</span>做乜撚嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:09:12.000Z","msg":"少開post，打算方便大家睇啫，費事又話睇到好亂"},{"pid":"f1